	<!-- grav bow -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseGun">
		<defName>Quiver_Bow_Grav</defName>
		<label>Grav Bow</label>
		<description>This modern less-lethal analog of the ancient selfbow is made from two low-grade anti-gravity pods (of the type sometimes used in star ships) mounted to a rigid frame. A virtual bowstring is superimposed in the appropriate location for user-friendliness. The grav bow has no moving parts. No arrow is fired; instead, a narrow gravity tunnel is projected in the direction of the enemy combatant. Test firings across multiple species (n=18,934) showed minor organ shock is nearly guaranteed. Documents accompanying the official techprint license plainly state "do not fire directly at the head." Cracked black market licenses rarely have these attachments.</description>
